title: Iron Kingdoms
description:
This is a full list of Iron Kingdoms books I've found throughout my time here.  Books include:

Core Rules
Unleashed Rules
Kings, Nations and Gods
Urban Adventures
Fools Rush In
A Quick Reference guide (for in combat actions and reminders)
A Self-Compiled Career PDF alphabatizing all the careers from the collected books
The full release of Full Metal Friday (including another self-complied PDF of all FMF releases in one convenient file)
Monsternomicon (including original d20 books)
No Quarter 48 (featuring the Convergence of Cyriss)
And, of course, sheets, sheets, sheets (and templates)
